site_name: Phase 3 of the Green Man Lane Regeneration Masterplan
description: Reserved matters application for Phase 3 of the Green Man Lane Estate masterplan detailing Landscaping and Appearance in relation to the construction of seven no. three-storey high terrace houses and two apartment buildings varying between six and eight storeys high containing 129 residential units (136 units in total including the terrace houses); provision of publicly accessible open space; private and semi-private amenity space, refuse/recycling and bicycle storage facilities; alterations to the adopted highway and provision of car parking following the demolition of Melrose Court, Buckfast Court, Nos. 2-6 Romsey Road and Nos. 2-34 Williams Road. Application made part pursuant to conditions 2 (Reserved Matters), 3 (Plans), 6 (Details of the proposed buildings), 9 (Details of the Code for Sustainable Homes) and 19 (Refuse and Recycling Enclosures) of the amended outline planning permission LBE ref: P/2013/4408 dated 07/11/2013 for the multi-Phased regeneration of the Green Man Lane Estate.
site_number: Phase 3 of the Green Man Lane Regeneration Masterplan
